com.microsoft.azure.documentdb

Class ResourceResponse<T extends Resource>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.ResourceResponse<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the resource type of the resource response.

    public final class ResourceResponse<T extends Resource>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the service response to a request made from DocumentClient in the Azure DocumentDB database service. Contains both the resource and the response headers.
